BRIEF-Lock-up period for Jiangsu Changjiang Electronics' 131.4 mln shares to end Sept 25 
Sept 25 Jiangsu Changjiang Electronics Technology Co Ltd 
* Says lock-up period for 131.4 million shares to end, trading to start on Oct 8
